{"service_name": "Design and Implementation of a Cloud-based Shared Service Centre", "service_id": "7359508827328608", "company_name": "Deloitte LLP", "page_content": "<main id=\"content\" role=\"main\">\n <div class=\"grid-row\">\n  <div class=\"column-two-thirds\">\n   <header class=\"page-heading-smaller\">\n    <p class=\"context\">\n     Deloitte LLP\n    </p>\n    <h1>\n     Design and Implementation of a Cloud-based Shared Service Centre\n    </h1>\n   </header>\n  </div>\n </div>\n <div class=\"grid-row\">\n  <div class=\"column-two-thirds\">\n   <p class=\"service-summary-lede\">\n    Deloitte will support you to implement a shared service solution to establish leading Finance, HR, Payroll and Procurement shared services operations for your organisation and potentially others.\r\nThe solution is based on SAP and offers web-enabled self-service applications, taking advantage of cloud-enabled technologies and complies with public sector security requirements.\n   </p>\n   <h2 class=\"service-summary-heading\">\n    Features\n   </h2>\n   <ul class=\"service-summary-features-and-benefits\">\n    <li>\n     Leading practise and standardised processes\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Shared service centre operating model\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Ability to host services for other organisations\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Cloud-enabled technology\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Web-enabled self-service applications for employees, vendors and customers\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Shared service centre organisation structure, roles and governance arrangements\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Robust project management processes\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     SAP and other web-enabled technologies\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Tools and methodologies\n    </li>\n   </ul>\n   <h2 class=\"service-summary-heading\">\n    Benefits\n   </h2>\n   <ul class=\"service-summary-features-and-benefits\">\n    <li>\n     Establish leading practice shared services operations\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Efficient support services\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Improved and increased self-service through web enabled technologies\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Standardised processes\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Reduced hand-offs and manual intervention\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Improved quality of data and management information\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Support services systems  integrated with core line of business systems\n    </li>\n   </ul>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"column-one-third\">\n   <div id=\"meta\">\n    <h2 class=\"visuallyhidden\">\n     Pricing\n    </h2>\n    <p class=\"price\">\n     \u00a3550 per unit per day\n    </p>\n    <ul class=\"price-caveats\">\n     <li>\n      Excluding VAT\n     </li>\n     <li>\n      Minimum contract period: Day\n     </li>\n    </ul>\n    <h2 class=\"visuallyhidden\">\n     Service documents\n    </h2>\n    <ul class=\"document-list\">\n     <li class=\"document-list-item\">\n      <a class=\"document-link-with-icon\" href=\"https://assets.digitalmarketplace.service.gov.uk/g-cloud-7/documents/92485/7359508827328608-pricing-document-2015-09-30-1605.pdf\">\n       <span class=\"document-icon\">\n        pdf\n        <span>\n         document:\n        </span>\n       </span>\n       Pricing\n      </a>\n     </li>\n     <li class=\"document-list-item\">\n      <a class=\"document-link-with-icon\" href=\"https://assets.digitalmarketplace.service.gov.uk/g-cloud-7/documents/92485/7359508827328608-service-definition-document-2015-09-30-1545.pdf\">\n       <span class=\"document-icon\">\n        pdf\n        <span>\n         document:\n        </span>\n       </span>\n       Service definition\n      </a>\n     </li>\n     <li class=\"document-list-item\">\n      <a class=\"document-link-with-icon\" href=\"https://assets.digitalmarketplace.service.gov.uk/g-cloud-7/documents/92485/7359508827328608-terms-and-conditions-2015-09-30-1550.pdf\">\n       <span class=\"document-icon\">\n        pdf\n        <span>\n         document:\n       